name: SVGClipPathElement
description: The SVGClipPathElement interface provides access to the properties of <clipPath> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.

members.name: SVGClipPathElement.clipPathUnits
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the clipPathUnits attribute of the given <clipPath> element. Takes one of the constants defined in SVGUnitTypes.
